title: SPORE.Creature.Creator-ViTALiTY
description:
Unleash your Creature Creativity! 

How do you feel about tentacles? Why only two eyes? Create
your own unique creatures and watch  them  come  to  life,
then share them with the world!
BUILD using 228 drag-and-drop,  flexible  parts  -  is  it
fashion, function, or fashunction?
PAINT with unique patterns, make your creature  stand  out
in a crowd.
PLAY with your creature as it comes to life  with  dances,
poses, and emotions.
SHARE using built-in snapshot and video tools - make  your
creature a star!
